Title: "Love\u2764"
DateModified: '2018-02-12'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/love
SetInCountry: Australia
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: Momina Mohiuddin
AuthorCountry: India
Text: Love...love is sumthg very unique and hard to find..bt the last thing i expected
  was i wil ever find my love tht too ocean's faraway..my life was colourless bt love
  filled my colours painted my walls of emty life wit love...gave me reason to survive
  when i had no reason too..filled my life wit passion..happiness an what not..today
  im a women with courageous attitude..everyone says every successful man has a women
  behind him...bt for me thr is a man behind my happy life...he lighted up my dark
  life..he gave life to my son...he is the most precious gift from heaven..he is an
  Angel....a man with beautiful soul...he touched my soul and our souls are deeply
  connected..i will always follow his steps an be behind his shadow...i had almost
  forgot hw to dream an dreams are always dreams but guess what dreams do come true
  if u truly belive god exits..he is an angel who has covered me in his wings an protected
  me from all the evil..an troubles an tht my man..my strength..my love..my world
  my hubby
